---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/about.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Estrelis.ai" description="Built by planners, for planners. Learn about the team behind the AI-native equipment planning platform.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <h1>Built by Planners, for Planners</h1>
    <p>We've spent years in the trenches of healthcare equipment planning. Estrelis is the tool we always wished existed.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <div class="mission-text">
      <p>Healthcare facilities are among the most complex buildings in the world. Every operating room, imaging suite, and patient room requires carefully coordinated equipment — often hundreds of thousands of items across a single project. Yet the industry still relies on fragmented spreadsheets, disconnected email chains, and manual catalog lookups.</p>
      <p>Estrelis exists to change that. We're building the first AI-native platform purpose-built for medical equipment planning — replacing manual processes with intelligent automation at every step, from initial room planning through procurement and installation.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="values">
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>AI-First</h3>
        <p>Every feature is designed with AI at the core, not bolted on as an afterthought.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>Healthcare-Native</h3>
        <p>Built specifically for medical equipment, not adapted from generic project management tools.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>Practitioner-Designed</h3>
        <p>Designed by equipment planners who understand the real workflow, not just the theory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Want to learn more?</h2>
    <p>We'd love to show you what Estrelis can do for your next project.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
